    "course_title": "FUNDAMENTALS OF INDUSTRIAL DATA ANALYTICS",
    "description": "Provides an understanding of the fundamentals of using data analytics to make data-driven decisions. Emphasizes applying techniques to industrial engineering problems. Focuses on formulating and solving real industrial problems with the appropriate modeling strategies and analytics principles for better decision making.",
